snippet.title: Reboot - Superfly DX (Atari Jaguar Game)
snippet.description:
http://reboot.atari.org

Reboot are part of the most active development team and community working on Atari Jaguar - Jagware. We also produce games and tools for the Atari ST/Falcon series of computers. As individuals we have been active on Atari machines since the mid-eighties. As a group we aim to produce fun, playable games and develop tools & utilities we need need as we progress. We're Atari fans from way back when - 2D Atari gaming is what we know & love & the Jaguar makes it fun and simple. We're not out to make super-spectacular epics, rather we aim for rock solid 50/60Hz fun of a more traditional nature, adding our own little twist to things as we go.
